-- 1. Sinews Multilingual Therapy - Seville
('Sinews Multilingual Therapy Institute - Seville', 'Mental Health', 'International multilingual therapy centre with Seville location offering comprehensive mental health services for English-speaking expats and international clients. Team of native English-speaking psychologists, psychiatrists, and therapists providing individual therapy, couples counseling, family therapy, and psychiatric consultations. Specializes in anxiety, depression, adjustment difficulties, and trauma therapy for expats. Also offers psycho-educational assessments for children and adults including ADHD and dyslexia evaluations. Both in-person sessions in Seville city center and online therapy options available. Professional team experienced in cross-cultural mental health issues.', 'Calle Imagen, 8, 1º, 41004', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 954 21 67 89', 'sevilla@sinews.es', 'https://www.sinews.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

