('Psicología Sevilla - English Speaking Psychologists', 'Mental Health', 'Team of bilingual English-Spanish psychologists in Seville providing therapy and counseling services for expats and international residents. Specializes in anxiety disorders, depression, stress management, relationship issues, and life transitions. Individual and couples therapy available with culturally-sensitive approach for international clients. Modern therapy rooms in central Seville with flexible scheduling including evening appointments. Online therapy sessions available for those preferring remote support. Professional registration with Colegio Oficial de Psicólogos de Andalucía.', 'Avenida de la Constitución, 22, 3º B, 41004', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 955 34 56 78', 'info@psicologiasevilla.es', 'https://www.psicologiasevilla.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 3. Centro de Psicología Integral Sevilla
('Centro de Psicología Integral Sevilla', 'Mental Health', 'Psychology center in Seville offering English-speaking therapy services for the international community. Licensed psychologists providing cognitive-behavioral therapy, mindfulness-based approaches, and integrative psychotherapy. Expertise in expat adjustment, cultural adaptation, work-related stress, and family dynamics. Individual therapy, couples counseling, and family sessions available. Located in the Nervión district with easy access by metro. Offers both face-to-face and video consultation options. Sliding scale fees available for certain circumstances.', 'Calle Luis de Morales, 18, 2º, 41005', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 954 98 76 54', 'contacto@cpisevilla.com', 'https://www.cpisevilla.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 4. Mente Serena - English Therapy Seville
('Mente Serena - English Therapy Seville', 'Mental Health', 'Boutique mental health practice in Seville specializing in English-language therapy for expats and international professionals. Founder is a UK-trained psychotherapist offering individual counseling, relationship therapy, and coaching. Focus areas include anxiety, depression, burnout, grief, and major life transitions. Warm, confidential environment in the historic Santa Cruz neighborhood. Flexible appointment times including weekends. Online therapy available throughout Spain. Experience working with diverse international clientele from North America, UK, Australia, and Northern Europe.', 'Calle Mateos Gago, 12, 1º A, 41004', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 679 45 23 12', 'hello@menteserena.es', 'https://www.menteserena.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 5. Clínica Psicológica Alameda
('Clínica Psicológica Alameda', 'Mental Health', 'Established psychology clinic in Seville with English-speaking staff serving the international community. Comprehensive mental health services including psychological evaluation, psychotherapy, and crisis intervention. Specializes in treating anxiety, mood disorders, eating disorders, and addiction recovery. Team includes clinical psychologists and psychiatric support for medication management when needed. Located near the Alameda de Hércules in the Macarena district. Accepts international health insurance from major providers. Emergency appointments available.', 'Calle Trajano, 25, Bajo, 41002', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 954 90 12 34', 'alameda@clinicapsicologica.es', 'https://www.clinicapsicologica.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 6. Wellbeing Seville - Mental Health & Wellness
('Wellbeing Seville - Mental Health & Wellness', 'Mental Health', 'Holistic mental health center in Seville combining psychological therapy with wellness services for English-speaking residents. Multidisciplinary team of psychologists, counselors, and wellness practitioners. Services include individual therapy, couples counseling, stress management programs, and mindfulness courses. Special interest in supporting digital nomads, remote workers, and retirees adjusting to life in Spain. Modern facilities in Triana district with views of the Guadalquivir River. Online booking system with evening and weekend availability. Most major international insurance accepted.', 'Calle Betis, 58, 3º, 41010', 'Seville', 'Seville', '+34 955 78 90 12', 'info@wellbeingseville.com', 'https://www.wellbeingseville.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
